reviewText: Love this workout, please issue a DVD of this.
Not a good workout for training core although to be fair, it probably was in its time.
Best workout for stomach.  Just wished this was on DVD.  Use older VHS player in basement so I can workout with this.
This is a great VHS, I love working out to it and ordered a backup just in case.

I have been using it for 3 weeks and it has been good for me. I had been sick a long time and use this tape to help me gain my strength back. The exercises are easy enough for me to do yet I still get a work out. I like that it says to do only 2 to 3 times a week as I find that easier to do then every day.

I love this workout. All through it Michelle gives good safety tips. I love how she has you hold at the contraction. You really feel your abs working. The 15 minutes goes by very quickly. I love how you also work your legs and butt as well as your abs.
